_sText:
"gg_tnb_desert"

Custom map made for: www.tnbgaming.net

This is a small sized symmetrical Gun Game map.
Buy Zones are included for Fight Yard style play too.

Please download, comment and enjoy!

- 48 Spawns
- Cubemaps
- Optimized for better FPS
- Overview radar map
- 3d skybox
- Buy Zones for non-gg play
- Nav File for bots
- Pakrated into one .bsp file
- Custom Textures from www.cgtextures.com


Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
